subtitle: Graphic Artist - Web Designer - Illustrator
about-text-1: Freelancer is a free bootstrap theme created by Start Bootstrap.The download includes the complete source files including HTML,CSS, and JavaScript as well as optional SASS stylesheets for easycustomization.
about-text-2: You can create your own custom avatar for the masthead, change theicon in the dividers, and add your email address to the contactform to make it fully functional!
